					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Jameelah Lang</h4>
												<p>Jameelah Lang is an associate professor of English at Rockhurst University. Her fiction and nonfiction appear in <em>The Kenyon Review</em>, <em>The Cincinnati Review</em>, <em>Witness</em>, <em>Pleiades</em>, and elsewhere. Her work, including her memoir-in-progress, has received fellowships and support from MacDowell, Bread Loaf Writers’ Conference, Sewanee Writers’ Conference, VCCA, and the Hub City Writers Project.</p>
